cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MA, cs.IT 

This paper deals with a general model of decentralized stochastic control, which involves sharing information among controllers. This topic is closely related to several sub-fields of computer science, including systems and control (cs.SY), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), multi-agent systems (cs.MA), and information theory (cs.IT). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper. Among these, cs.SY is the most likely sub-category as the paper deals with control systems.
